nelix (0.1.0-5) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add a strict source-tree real user manifest NeLisp runtime gate.
  * Include the standalone-safe balanced JSON list builder for Nelix fast
    paths.
  * Run the installed CLI autopkgtest verifier with bash explicitly.
  * Let source-tree init migration checks skip installed Debian package
    version preflight explicitly.
